1, à Bretagne, France, fils d’Earl Ralph. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Gytha Countess of Hereford. Il est décédé le 21 décembre 1096, à l’âge de 86 ans."},"de":{"about 1011–21 December 1096":"um 1011–21. Dezember 1096","1011–1096":"1011–1096","1059–1096":"1059–1096","1026–1099":"1026–1099","1039–1096":"1039–1096","1073–Male":"1073–Verstorben","1096–Male":"1096–Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","about 1096":"um 1096","1039":"1039","21 December 1096":"21. Dezember 1096","1026":"1026","1059":"1059","about 1039":"um 1039","1099":"1099","1011":"1011","before 1096":"vor 1096","1096":"1096","1073":"1073","about 1011":"um 1011","Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Angevin Empire":"Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Frankreich","Brittany, France":"Bretagne, Frankreich","On the way to Palestine for the First Crusade":"Northamptonshire, England","Bretagne, France":"Bretagne, Frankreich","Palestine":"Palästina","lifeSummary":"Ralph de Gael The Staller Earl of Suffolk and Norfolk wurde um 1011 in Bretagne, Frankreich, als Sohn von Earl Ralph geboren. Er hatte mit Gytha Countess of Hereford mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb am 21. Dezember 1096 im Alter von 86 Jahren."},"ht":{"about 1011–21 December 1096":"about 1011–21 December 1096","1011–1096":"1011–1096","1059–1096":"1059–1096","1026–1099":"1026–1099","1039–1096":"1039–1096","1073–Male":"1073–Desede","1096–Male":"1096–Desede","–Male":"Desede","about 1096":"about 1096","1039":"1039","21 December 1096":"21 December 1096","1026":"1026","1059":"1059","about 1039":"about 1039","1099":"1099","1011":"1011","before 1096":"before 1096","1096":"1096","1073":"1073","about 1011":"about 1011","Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Angevin Empire":"Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, France","Brittany, France":"Bretagne, France","On the way to Palestine for the First Crusade":"Northamptonshire, England","Bretagne, France":"Bretagne, France","Palestine":"Palästina"},"hu":{"about 1011–21 December 1096":"1011 körül–1096. december 21.","1011–1096":"1011–1096","10