t-Vilaine, Bretagne, Francia","Brittany, France":"Bretagne, Francia","On the way to Palestine for the First Crusade":"Northamptonshire, England","Bretagne, France":"Bretagne, Francia","Palestine":"Palestina","lifeSummary":"Ralph de Gael The Staller Earl of Suffolk and Norfolk è nato il circa 1011 nel Bretagne, Francia come figlio di Earl Ralph. Lui avuto almeno 1 figlio con Gytha Countess of Hereford. Morì il 21 dicembre 1096, all'età di 86 anni."},"ja":{"about 1011–21 December 1096":"約1011年–1096年12月21日","1011–1096":"1011年–1096年","1059–1096":"1059年–1096年","1026–1099":"1026年–1099年","1039–1096":"1039年–1096年","1073–Male":"1073年–死亡","1096–Male":"1096年–死亡","–Male":"死亡","about 1096":"約1096年","1039":"1039年","21 December 1096":"1096年12月21日","1026":"1026年","1059":"1059年","about 1039":"約1039年","1099":"1099年","1011":"1011年","before 1096":"1096年以前","1096":"1096年","1073":"1073年","about 1011":"約1011年","Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Angevin Empire":"フランスブレタグンイレ-エト-ヴィレアインガeル","Brittany, France":"フランスブレタグン","On the way to Palestine for the First Crusade":"イギリスノーサンプトンシュアイア","Bretagne, France":"フランスブレタグン","Palestine":"パレスチナ","lifeSummary":"Ralph de Gael The Staller Earl of Suffolk and Norfolkは約1011年にフランスブレタグンでEarl Ralphの息子として生まれた。彼はGytha Countess of Herefordとの間に少なくとも1人の息子をもうけた。彼は1096年12月21日に86歳で死去した。"},"ko":{"about 1011–21 December 1096":"대략 1011년–1096년 12월 21일","1011–1096":"1011년–1096년","1059–1096":"1059년–1096년","1026–1099":"1026년–1099년","1039–1096":"1039년–1096년","1073–Male":"1073년–사망","1096–Male":"1096년–사망","–Male":"사망","about 1096":"대략 1096년","1039":"1039년","21 December 1096":"1096년 12월 21일","1026":"1026년","1059":"1059년","about 1039":"대략 1039년","1099":"1099년","1011":"1011년","before 1096":"1096년 이전","1096":"1096년","1073":"1073년","about 1011":"대략 1011년","Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Angevin Empire":"프랑스 브레타그니 이레-트-빌레이인 가e","Brittany, France":"프랑스 브레타그니","On the way to Palestine for the First Crusade":"영국 노르섬프토실르","Bretagne, France":"프랑스 브레타그니","Palestine":"팔레스타인","lifeSummary":"Ralph de Gael The Staller Earl of Suffolk and Norfolk(은)는 대략 1011년 프랑스 브레타그니에서 Earl Ralph의 아들로 태어났다. 그는 Gytha Countess of Hereford(와)과 적어도 한 명의 아들을 두었다. 그는 1096년 12월 21일 86세의 나이로 사망했다."},"lv":{"about 1011–21 December 1096":"ap 1011. gadu–1096. gada 21. decembris","1011–1096":"1011–1096.gads","1059–1096":"1059–1096.gads","1026–1099":"1026–1099","1039–1096":"1039–1096.gads","1073–Male":"1073.gads–miris","1096–Male":"1096.gads–miris","–Male":"miris","about 1096":"ap 1096. gadu","1039":"1039","21 December 1096":"1096. gada 21. decembris","1026":"1026","1059":"1059","about 1039":"ap 1039. gadu","1099":"1099","1011":"1011","before 1096":"pirms 1096. gada","1096":"1096. gads","1073":"1073. gads","about 1011":"ap 1011. gadu","Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Angevin Empire":"Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Francija","Brittany, France":"Bretagne, Francija","On the way to Palestine for the First Crusade":"Northamptonshire, England","Bretagne, France":"Bretagne, Francija","Palestine":"Palestīna"},"mg":{"about 1011–21 December 1096":"tany ho any amin'ny 1011–21 desambra 1096","1011–1096":"1011–1096","1059–1096":"1059–1096","1026–1099":"1026–1099","1039–1096":"1039–1096","1073–Male":"1073–Maty","1096–Male":"1096–Maty","–Male":"Maty","about 1096":"tany ho any amin'ny 1096","1039":"1039","21 December 1096":"21 desambra 1096","1026":"1026","1059":"1059","about 1039":"tany ho any amin'ny 1039","1099":"1099","1011":"1011","before 1096":"talohan'ny 1096","1096":"1096","1073":"1073","about 1011":"tany ho any amin'ny 1011","Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Angevin Empire":"Gaël, Ille-et-Vilaine, Bretagne, Frantsa","Brittany, France":"Bretagne, Frantsa","On the way to Palestine for the First Crusade":"Northamptonshire, England","Bretagne, France":"Bretagne, Frantsa","Palestine":"Palästina"},"ms":{"about 1011–21 December 1096":"kira–kira 1011–21 Disember 1096","1011–1096":"1011–1096","1059–1096":"1059–1096","1026–1099":"1026–1099","1039–1096":"1039–1096","1073–Male":"1073–Mati","1096–M